com.cyc.session

Interface EnvironmentConfiguration

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CycSessionConfiguration
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EnvironmentConfigurationLoader.EnvironmentConfigurationImpl

    public interface EnvironmentConfiguration
extends CycSessionConfiguration
    A CycSessionConfiguration drawn specifically from the System properties. An instance of EnvironmentConfiguration is a snapshot of the relevant System properties from the time at which it was created. EnvironmentConfigurations always take precedence over all over configurations, except to the extent that an EnvironmentConfiguration may specify another configuration.
